			<h3>Challenge - Creating An Artificially Intelligent Opponent</h3>

			<p class="project-description">
			Implementing a computer algorithm that could win at tic-tac-toe was challenging, let alone implementing an efficient algorithm that pursued two key goals of a) strategically making moves based on an opponent's most recent move, and b) knowing when to stop blocking opponent's moves if the opportunity to win presented itself.
			</p>
